---
import '../styles/About.css'
---

<section id="about">
  <p class="about-label reveal">// who am i</p>
  <h2 class="about-title reveal">About Me</h2>
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-left reveal">
      <img src="/images/pfp.png" alt="Sky" class="about-pfp" />
    </div>
    <div class="about-right">
      <div class="about-text reveal">
        <p>I'm <strong>Sutanu K. Majumder</strong>, a <strong>Self-Taught Programmer</strong> from West Bengal, India. Most people online know me by the name NotNightSky or simply Sky. I initially got into programming because I wanted to mod the game known as <strong>Minecraft</strong>, which has now led me to learn more about programming and about computers generally.</p>
        <p>I write mods and plugins in java using FabricMC and PaperMC, adding new mechanics and QoL features or whatever I need to play the game. When I am not modding the game, I like to explore new web technologies.</p>
        <p>Everything I know came from <strong>Reading docs, watching tutorial, trial and error, and from people whom I call friends</strong>. I believe the best way to learn is to actually build useful projects instead of watching tutorials</p>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-grid">
        <div class="stat-card reveal">
          <span class="stat-num">2+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years Coding</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card reveal">
          <span class="stat-num">5+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Mods Created</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card reveal">
          <span class="stat-num">3+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Contributions</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>